room_title: Escape room "Shipwrecked with St. Paul" by Bible Treks Christian Escape Room in Denver
room_description: Join St. Paul on his incredible journey to Rome as he becomes shipwrecked on the island of Malta! A journey right out of the book of Acts Ch. 27-28, join St. Paul in his quest to spread the gospel of Jesus Christ! Hop into Scripture as you and your team join St. Paul on this Biblical Epic!
